{"tha-ap356:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap356:0.2":"Saddasannakavagga ","tha-ap356:0.3":"4 Sakosakakorandadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap356:1.1":"“Akkantanca padam disva, ","tha-ap356:1.2":"sikhino lokabandhuno; ","tha-ap356:1.3":"Ekamsam ajinam katva, ","tha-ap356:1.4":"padasettham avandaham. ","tha-ap356:2.1":"Korandam pupphitam disva, ","tha-ap356:2.2":"padapam dharaniruham; ","tha-ap356:2.3":"Sakosakam gahetvana, ","tha-ap356:2.4":"padacakkam apujayim. ","tha-ap356:3.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap356:3.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap356:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap356:3.4":"padapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap356:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap356:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap356:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap356:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sakosakakorandadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap356:6.1":"Sakosakakorandadayakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}